{"tid":1250246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左勿分化，勿割蓆，勿篤灰","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T14:10:19.000Z","uid":155837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95045516ca4e802a446f41d3497712c37ef2c099","tid":1250246,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:09:15.000Z","msg":"係咪仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿聆聽，勿溝通</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係嘅話，大家喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">討論區</span></span>討論嘅時候可唔可以聽下大家講野？聽完你可以唔認同，可以唔跟。<br />\n<br />\n你有你嘅道理，唔代表佢冇道理，有好多野唔係非黑即白，依個就係點解唔要大台，而要集體智慧嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子，有人叫你地走，分析俾你聽點解要走，你唔認同要走你可以唔走，有其他人認同要走所以咪走。你覺得唔走先係啱嘅，你咪說服人唔好走，就係咁簡單。"},{"pid":"50c200c1f1432f148a1a230bec2587e5af6d1610","tid":1250246,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"113593a6e6349f693cf311d2bdc388fb3e7c9afa","tid":1250246,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001e5c3709e5335f951f4c10ca77af64130b7bca","tid":1250246,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"都係果句，要走要留自己決定<br />\n目標一致，各有各做"},{"pid":"10b560490e6f31dbd84d33d836fe417010f804d3","tid":1250246,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"推 歷史總係不斷重複 勿分化唔係籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}